<li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feMorphology\"><code>&lt;feMorphology&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feOffset\"><code>&lt;feOffset&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/fePointLight\"><code>&lt;fePointLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpotLight\"><code>&lt;feSpotLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTile\"><code>&lt;feTile&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTurbulence\"><code>&lt;feTurbulence&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face\"><code>&lt;font-face&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-format\"><code>&lt;font-face-format&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-name\"><code>&lt;font-face-name&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-src\"><code>&lt;font-face-src&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-uri\"><code>&lt;font-face-uri&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>G\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/g\"><code>&lt;g&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>H\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/hkern\"><code>&lt;hkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>I\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>J-L\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/linearGradient\"><code>&lt;linearGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>M\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/metadata\"><code>&lt;metadata&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mpath\"><code>&lt;mpath&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>N-P\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>Q-R\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>S\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section>\n<p>The <strong><code>direction</code></strong> attribute specifies the inline-base direction of a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a> element. It defines the start and end points of a line of text as used by the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/text-anchor\">text-anchor</a></code> and <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/inline-size\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">inline-size</a></code> properties. It also may affect the direction in which characters are positioned if the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/unicode-bidi\">unicode-bidi</a></code> property's value is either <code>embed</code> or <code>bidi-override</code>.</p>\n<p>It applies only to glyphs oriented perpendicular to the inline-base direction, which includes the usual case of horizontally-oriented Latin or Arabic text and the case of narrow-cell Latin or Arabic characters rotated 90 degrees clockwise relative to a top-to-bottom inline-base direction.</p>\n<p>In many cases, the bidirectional Unicode algorithm produces the desired result automatically, so this attribute doesn't need to be specified in those cases. For other cases, such as when using right-to-left languages, it may be sufficient to add the <code>direction</code> attribute to the outermost <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a> element, and allow that direction to inherit to all text elements:</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> As a presentation attribute, <code>direction</code> can be used as a CSS property. See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/direction\"><code>css direction</code></a> for further information.</p>\n</div>\n<p>You can use this attribute with the following SVG elements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/altGlyph\"><code>&lt;altGlyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css hidden notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">html,\nbody,\nsvg</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 600 72<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rtl<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>fa<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>text</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>300<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">text-anchor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>middle<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">font-size</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>36<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    داستان SVG 1.1 SE طولا ني است.\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_notes","title":"Usage notes","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n      <td><code>ltr</code> | <code>rtl</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n      <td><code>ltr</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-writing-modes/#direction","title":"CSS Writing Modes Level 4"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/text.html#DirectionProperty","title":"Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)"}],"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.direction"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.direction","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/direction/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/direction\"><code>css direction</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Usage notes","id":"usage_notes"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The direction attribute specifies the inline-base direction of a <text> or <tspan> element. It defines the start and end points of a line of text as used by the text-anchor and inline-size properties. It also may affect the direction in which characters are positioned if the unicode-bidi property's value is either embed or bidi-override.","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-09-14T09:21:13.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/svg/attribute/direction","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/svg/attribute/direction/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/f42cbd9709e5c61e3d4833f6d911aae9bed5275d","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG Attribute reference"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/direction","title":"direction"}],"pageTitle":"direction - SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics | MDN","noIndexing":false}}